	<files>
		<file filename="JQueryHoverIntent.lib.php" md5="aee32463fa0e30a75179e374e21ca641">
			<class name="JQueryHoverIntent"/>
		</file>
	</files>
	<description>
		hoverIntent is a plug-in that attempts to determine the user's intent...
		like a crystal ball, only with mouse movement! It works like (and was derived from)
		jQuery's built-in hover. However, instead of immediately calling the onMouseOver function,
		it waits until the user's mouse slows down enough before making the call.
	</description>
